    }else{
      add(`Mix on low until combined and the ${label} begins to strengthen${hasOil?`, then add the ${gW(I.oil)} oil gradually`:""}. Continue with the ${mixMode==="spiral"?"spiral mixer for a total of about 4–6 minutes":"stand mixer for a total of about 6–8 minutes"}, stopping when the ${label} is smooth, elastic and has the strength required for the style.`+why("Mechanical mixing develops gluten quickly but also warms the dough. Stop at development rather than treating the clock as a target."+(hotMachine?" The kitchen is warm enough that checking the finished dough temperature is particularly important.":"")),mins(mixMode==="spiral"?7:9));
