      return `Plan the preheat now. The ${ovenType==="pizza"?"pizza oven":"oven"} and ${surface} must be fully at ${tF(ovenTemp)} when proof ends. A home-oven steel or stone usually needs 45–60 minutes after the oven is switched on; start before shaping when the proof window is shorter than that.`;
