    ? "A spiral mixer works the dough hardest and fastest \u2014 about 4\u20135 minutes. It develops and warms the dough sooner, so watch the dough temperature in a warm kitchen."
    : "A stand mixer builds the gluten up front \u2014 about 6\u20138 minutes to a smooth, elastic dough.";
}
